[[File:TipocaCity-CC.png|thumb|250px|Tipoca City on Kamino was inspired by the Alderaanian Oversea architecture.]]
'''Alderaanian Oversea''' was a form of [[City/Legends|city]] construction that originated from [[Alderaan/Legends|Alderaan]] wherein cities were built on stilts in the shallow [[Salt/Legends|saline]] [[Ocean/Legends|seas]]. A manifestation of Alderaanian desire to build their cities as a part of the environment, the concept was used in [[Tipoca City/Legends|Tipoca City]] and many other stilt-cities on [[Kamino/Legends|Kamino]], although their stilts were significantly taller due to the much-deeper oceans on that [[Planet/Legends|world]].

